.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH completion 1  "completion " 
.SH NAME
completion \- Generate or install shell completions
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmurk completion\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] <\fIsubcommands\fR>
.SH DESCRIPTION
Generate or install shell completions
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
completion\-generate(1)
Print completions to stdout
.TP
completion\-install(1)
Install completions to the standard path
.TP
completion\-help(1)
Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)
